1. *Radila* je u banci tri godine. (She worked in the bank for three years.) 
2. Ona je *radila* u školi pre nego što je otišla u penziju. (She worked in the school before she retired.) 
3. Njena majka je *radila* kao lekarka. (Her mother worked as a doctor.)
4. On je *radio* u trgovini pre nego što je počeo da radi na selu. (He worked in a store before he started working on the farm.)
5. Kada je bio mlad, *radila* je kao konobar. (When he was young, he worked as a waiter.)